{"tid":1362283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB員工貼連儂牆寫「他朝君體也相同」　遭保安員立即清場","createTime":"2019-07-24T23:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T00:56:33.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"732bb4c27b787a945819805519904ba9c15aa1e1","tid":1362283,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T23:35:48.000Z","msg":"最近一連串的社會事件，實在令人相當痛心，尤以昨日元朗出現大量兇徒無差別攻擊市民，連特首都話令人髮指。市民一直為這場社會活動不停發聲，甚至每區都有自設的連儂牆，雖然間中有另一批市民上前拆毀，但不停又有人重建，野草燒不盡。<br />\n周一(22日)，竟然有TVB員工鼓起勇氣於公司新聞部內建立連儂牆，依相片所見，該連儂牆只有幾張memo紙，數量並不多，相信TVB管理人員非常重視，立即叫保安上前進行清場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3065416/org/38030683becce8191563597d084cc504.jpeg/rBBEq8o8Man-V6dEGsJhb6gGMQkEQFdwj7Weu6m1nrs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3065416%2Forg%2F38030683becce8191563597d084cc504.jpeg%2FrBBEq8o8Man-V6dEGsJhb6gGMQkEQFdwj7Weu6m1nrs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=eceba0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3065417/org/a59ebebb09fb905fdb701f40ad9c6704.jpeg/33D8BdRONHseYaAyKHzVlVJ8j3_4_0k-SRAoC28QKAs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3065417%2Forg%2Fa59ebebb09fb905fdb701f40ad9c6704.jpeg%2F33D8BdRONHseYaAyKHzVlVJ8j3_4_0k-SRAoC28QKAs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7d864ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f7eeb08068967488d5a8b18ce970554b58a6005","tid":1362283,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T23:59:51.000Z","msg":"食蕉九成係退休龜"},{"pid":"bd6b0e8b2415d771f05797d096ce997972f7c6f7","tid":1362283,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:01:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fc786a72fe42498da84a7b112a1d944870497a0","tid":1362283,"uid":276383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T00:42:38.000Z","msg":"個個以為自己真係鐵面陳 lol"},{"pid":"7be0981399a50effccbf2c409f68ae7bb6a42f47","tid":1362283,"uid":191968,"like":0